title: PumpRules: It's Brittany, Bach — Live from Austin
description:
Hey guys — did you hear that Brittany and Jax are getting married? America's sourhearts bring all their friends down to Miami for a joint bachelor/bachelorette party on Vanderpump Rules, and the drama that ensues is... classic.
Seriously Brittany: don't do it!!!
